full_text:
I&#39;m willing to bet that if you heard any word more than once -- bitch especially -- this is a message.  If you neglect to say some sort of protection prayer before conducting your session, you are more likely to attract entities that use those kind of words.  In my experience (which is short), the entities will repeat words over and over, just so you can pick these words out and know you&#39;re not imagining them.  Look for patterns, and ask for nothing negative to come through during the session (although that doesn&#39;t always work).



